---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import radionicaImg from '~/assets/images/radionica.jpg';
---

<section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-6xl">
	<div class="grid gap-6 row-gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
		<div class="md:pb-6 md:pr-16">
			<h2 class="mb-8 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold font-heading">
				Projektne aktivnosti
			</h2>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
							<Icon name="tabler:arrow-down" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-slate-200" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
					<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Istraživanje percepcije važnosti mora</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
						Istraživanje percepcije važnosti mora kod djece viših i nižih razreda osnovne škole provesti će se prije svake radionice kroz kratki anketni upitnik.  
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
							<Icon name="tabler:arrow-down" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-slate-200" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
					<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Edukativne radionice</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
						Radionice će se sastojati od dva dijela: teoretskog i praktičnog. U teoretskom dijelu će se kroz interaktivne prezentacije obraditi različiti aspekti važnosti mora. U praktičnom dijelu radionice učenici će se upoznati s nekim od metoda u istraživanju mora te će zatim pod lupom gledati unaprijed pripremljene preparate (plankton, ličinke i larve riba, alge, razni histološki preparati, sediment i sl.). 
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
							<Icon name="tabler:arrow-down" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-slate-200" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
					<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Kreativne radionice</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
						Nakon edukativnih radionica učenike će se potaknuti na kreativno izražavanje da kroz crtež, fotografiju, kolaž, skulpturu, pjesmu ili video izraze svoje mišljenje/osjećaje o moru i njegovoj važnosti. 
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2 bg-primary-600">
							<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 text-white dark:text-slate-200" />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-1">
					<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Izložba dječjih radova</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400"></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="relative">
			<Image
				class="inset-0 object-cover object-top w-full rounded-md shadow-lg md:absolute md:h-full bg-gray-400 dark:bg-slate-700"
				src={radionicaImg}
				widths={[400, 768]}
				sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 432px"
				alt="Radionica"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
